body: Yeah, sucks when the art is great but the genre isn’t to your liking. There’s one artist whose work is amazing but it’s all scat which I’m not into lol. This artist’s most popular work on this site by a huge margin is Kyoudai Switch, which is just your typical incest hentai but the art, poses, and situations are all so hot.
This artist is pretty good, just his stories are full of fetishes that ain't my taste (NTR, 'otokonoko' or female dicks, etc).
